/* <orly/lang_tests/general/diag_mutable_type.orly>

   Diagnostics pin (issue #314): malformed `mutable` type expressions must
   produce clean end-user errors, not compiler assertion failures. This test
   is EXPECTED to fail compilation (tracked in .xfail); the .state baseline
   pins the exact messages.

